 <title>HiperTropicalDocumentando</title>
 <link>http://rede.metareciclagem.org/wiki/HiperTropicalDocumentando</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Documenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do EncontraoHiperTropical de MetaReciclagem:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://ubalab.org/blog/o-encontrao-hipertropical-de-metareciclagem&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;O Encontr&amp;atilde;o Hipertropical de Metareciclagem&lt;/a&gt;, post de efefe, mais &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.flickr.com/photos/felipefonseca/tags/hipertropical/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;fotos&lt;/a&gt; (flickr);&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://wiki.nosdigitais.teia.org.br/Oficina_5_-_ANGAA&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Documenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da Oficina&lt;/a&gt; no wiki do Pont&amp;atilde;o N&amp;oacute;s Digitais (e fotos &lt;a href=&quot;http://fotos.nosdigitais.teia.org.br/oficinas-abertas-encontrao-angaa/page/2&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;aqui&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=oa.307843099304499&amp;amp;type=1&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Fotos do prof. &amp;Aacute;lvaro&lt;/a&gt; (&amp;eacute;, facebook, desculpem)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=oa.306373096118166&amp;amp;type=1&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Fotos da Etec&lt;/a&gt; (tamb&amp;eacute;m facebook)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/folder/d/0B0tbriM1UVHfNF9IUmRYVGJUTlk/edit?pli=1&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Fotos&lt;/a&gt; e mais &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/folder/d/0B2fJgb8QsTO6VlhaZ2Etc005UDQ/edit&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;fotos&lt;/a&gt; (no google)&lt;/li&gt;
